  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Luck-Bonus\">luck bonus</a>&nbsp;on the saving throw type of your choice (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fortitude</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Will\">Will</a>). As a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Full-Round-Actions\">full-round action</a>, you can change which saving throw your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Luck-Bonus\">luck bonus</a>&nbsp;applies to. At 7th level and every 4 levels thereafter, this bonus increases by 1, to a maximum of +5 at 19th level.</p>"
